title: No. 5 Irish prepare to take on high-powered No. 2 Ohio State
description:
Wendi Nix, Greg McElroy, and Joey Galloway are joined by Holly Rowe, live from South Bend, to discuss the fifth-ranked Irish and how they are preparing for their trip down to Columbus to take on the No. 2 Ohio State Buckeyes Saturday night. Plus, the crew breaks down some other debuts they are excited for this weekend.
